    <item>
      <title>马修斯亚洲首席信息官泰勒谈美联储和亚洲市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-24/matthews-asia-cio-taylor-on-fed-asian-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Matthews Asia 首席投资官兼投资组合经理 Sean Taylor 讨论了美联储政策及其对亚洲经济和金融资产的影响。他还在“彭博社：中国秀”上分享了他对中国股票的看法。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-24/matthews-asia-cio-taylor-on-fed-asian-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 02:13:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛称澳洲联储降息的市场定价“太浅”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/goldman-says-market-pricing-for-rba-rate-cuts-is-too-shallow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团认为，货币市场对澳大利亚未来 12 个月降息的定价“太浅”，并预测通胀降温和失业率上升将迫使央行更早采取行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/goldman-says-market-pricing-for-rba-rate-cuts-is-too-shallow</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 02:12:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>开发商万科将获得11亿美元单位担保贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/developer-vanke-to-get-1-1-billion-of-loans-guaranteed-by-units</link>
      <description><![CDATA[万科公司表示，将获得由其子公​​司担保的 78 亿元人民币（11 亿美元）的银行贷款，以“满足业务运营需求”，因为这家现金紧张的开发商试图避免违约。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/developer-vanke-to-get-1-1-billion-of-loans-guaranteed-by-units</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 02:09:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Segantii 赎回请求在关闭前已达 10 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/segantii-redemption-requests-hit-1-billion-before-move-to-shut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，Segantii Capital Management Ltd. 的对冲基金在决定关闭之前面临近 10 亿美元的提款请求，这凸显了本月香港内幕交易指控对投资者信心的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/segantii-redemption-requests-hit-1-billion-before-move-to-shut</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 01:47:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>禽流感蔓延至澳大利亚维多利亚州第二个农场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/avian-flu-spreads-to-second-farm-in-australia-s-victoria-state</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据报道，为了遏制高致病性禽流感的爆发，澳大利亚东南部采取了检疫措施，数十万只产蛋鸡被扑杀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/avian-flu-spreads-to-second-farm-in-australia-s-victoria-state</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 01:45:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>米莱警告内阁的未来取决于阿根廷国会投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/milei-warns-cabinet-s-future-hinges-on-argentina-congress-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱周四警告说，他的整个内阁将接受审查，具体取决于他的亲商业改革法案在国会获得通过的结果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/milei-warns-cabinet-s-future-hinges-on-argentina-congress-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 01:41:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西尔克表示，新西兰联储“绝对”准备在必要时加息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/rbnz-absolutely-prepared-to-hike-rates-if-necessary-silk-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰央行助理行长凯伦·西尔克(Karen Silk)表示，如果经济发展意味着当前政策环境的限制性不足以使通胀回到目标水平，新西兰央行准备加息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/rbnz-absolutely-prepared-to-hike-rates-if-necessary-silk-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 01:39:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
